Product details

Nutritional Info

See more

Top highlights

  • Universal Compatibility: Designed to be compatible with most insulin pens, offering versatile use for various diabetes management needs.
  • Ultra Fine Needle: Triple sharpened, 3-beveled edge needle ensures painless, precise injections with minimal discomfort.
  • Optimized Liquid Flow: Integrated with thin wall technology, enabling smoother and faster insulin flow during injections.
  • Safe & Sterile: Undergoes EO sterilization to ensure each needle is free from contaminants and safe for every use.
  • Non-toxic & Non-pyrogenic: Crafted with the highest medical standards, ensuring that the needles are non-toxic and will not cause pyrogenic reactions.
